{"tid":2217967,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［數學師］數學疑問求解！","createTime":"2020-09-26T00:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T01:48:11.000Z","uid":192989,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf1bde4e6e8106bde0c356a8e78d144ba609f15","tid":2217967,"uid":192989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T00:51:01.000Z","msg":"點解一個數既所有數字總和可以除得盡3<br />\n本身果個數就一定除得盡3？<br />\n<br />\n例子： 777<br />\n7+7+7=21  （21除得盡3）<br />\n所以777本身都除得盡3🤔<br />\n<br />\n數學師請出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1668ce24c37c4003029439dca2c886b7b30f82f3","tid":2217967,"uid":370409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:03:15.000Z","msg":"因爲<br />\n<br />\n10 - 9 = 1<br />\n100 - 99 = 1<br />\n1000 - 999 = 1<br />\n<br />\nand so forth<br />\nthus,<br />\n<br />\nevery numeral in any digits of a number contributes by addition to the remainder when the number is divided by 3<br />\nwhen the remainders sum up to a multiple of 3<br />\nthe number is divisible by 3"},{"pid":"1e801239f7c209494f13ee2a92dfb2dd7f07d969","tid":2217967,"uid":140934,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:06:52.000Z","msg":"唔咁複雜，用樓主所講嘅3位數做例<br />\n假設一個數係abc<br />\n如果a+b+c=3N (N係整數)<br />\n則<br />\n100a+10b+c<br />\n=a+b+c+99a+9b<br />\n=3N+99a+9b<br />\n=3(N+33a+3b) 即係3嘅倍數"},{"pid":"8f70f38445c40bc8c4585822b939abf2b705a5b2","tid":2217967,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ac8a65fb0fde4b19ffa7db656701b6cb0a9f9e","tid":2217967,"uid":370409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:48:11.000Z","msg":"Extended Reading:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.yll.url.tw/viewtopic.php?t=34152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yll.url.tw%2Fviewtopic.php%3Ft%3D34152&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzi8TOYG